&lt;p&gt;The sophisticated cuisine at Le Calandre blends invigoratingly modern with the elegantly classic, which has earned it &lt;strong&gt;3 Michelin Stars&lt;/strong&gt;, is listed in&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;2016 World&rsquo;s 50 Best Restaurants at&nbsp;#39&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;#34 in the 2015 World&rsquo;s 50 Best Restaurants&lt;/strong&gt; and is &lt;strong&gt;#36 on The Elite 100&lt;/strong&gt;. The dining room is modern with impeccable attention to detail. Attire is business casual.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please &lt;a title=&quot;Le Calandre Reservations&quot; href=&quot;http://www.alajmo.it/prenota_web.asp?sezione=calandre&amp;amp;lingua=ing&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;book online&lt;/a&gt; or contact Le Calandre by phone at +39 049 630303 or email at info@alajmo.it to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: &nbsp;Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 48 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm. If you do not reconfirm, your reservation will be given away. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

